          "TITLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Measurement of cross sections for a-induced reactions",
                " on 197Au and thick-target yields for the (a,g)",
                " process on 64Zn and 63Cu"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "FACILITY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "CYCLO"
                ],
                "institute": "1USABRK"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " 88 In. Cyclotron at Lawrence Berkeley",
                " National Laboratory (LBNL)."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SPECT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Gold, zinc, and copper targets were bombarded with an",
                " alpha-beam (He+)",
                " Sample Energy Current Irradiation time   Total charge",
                "          (MeV) (microA) (hours)        (microC+/-5%)",
                " Au stack 24.0+/-0.3   1    6              20963",
                "          18.0+/-0.2   0.7  5              10221",
                " Zn       14.0+/-0.2   0.1  0.62             203",
                "          10.0+/-0.1   0.6  1               2158",
                "           8.8+/-0.1   1.5  2              10774",
                "           7.9+/-0.1   1.5  4              20783",
                "           7.0+/-0.1   1.8  7.08           33465",
                " Cu        7.0+/-0.1   1.4  1.25            6381"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The foils were mounted on circular aluminum holders.",
                " Two stacks were prepared with each having four gold",
                " targets interspaced by three aluminum foils of",
                " thickness about 7mg/cm2. A titanium sheet of",
                " 0.016 in. thickness was placed at the end of each",
                " stack. The target stacks were mounted on a thick",
                " water-cooled copper block.",
                "The gold foil contained 99.9% gold, 0.03% silver,",
                " 0.05% copper, and a few other trace elements."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "GE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Samples were counted with an HPGe detector",
                " immediately following the irradiation and later with",
                " another HPGe detector. The second HPGe detector was",
                " located at LBNL's Low Background Facility (LBF)."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "MONITOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The titanium sheet was used to measure the",
                " thick-target yield for the 48Ti(a,n)51Cr reaction.",
                " The measured yield was used to verify the beam",
                " current integration"
              ]
            }
          ],
